{"tid":701291,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"紀錄自己兩個月身體變化","createTime":"2018-06-14T04:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T17:02:23.000Z","uid":84384,"like":29,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"0603b4170a6c0c0aa02bd3780ba2897e7d563065","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:33:07.000Z","msg":"中學畢業之後就冇再點做運動 頂盡都係幾個月打次波 但第日全身酸到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n168 66.5kg 有肚腩 面型小小肥腫<br />\n做緊零售腰同肩都好易酸痛<br />\n仲有小小駝背 要成日提自己挺直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n短期打算堅持落街跑步 <br />\n返工都早啲起身跑一跑<br />\n未諗住戒食 但唔飲汽水<br />\n<br />\n睇下兩個月身體會唔會有所改善 <br />\n最希望係個肚腩縮咁啲既 著衫slim小小都怕尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f729a2185d64acb712f3b0306534860ea6cd21","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":5,"dislike":45,"score":-40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:34:21.000Z","msg":"Day1 落左街跑15分鐘<br />\n對腳好撚酸 沖完涼返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望今晚可以堅持跑多轉 叫做跑半個鍾呃下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12657c274960ed68e6c0cadc15e882fc8512ac4c","tid":701291,"uid":54927,"like":14,"dislike":15,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:35:16.000Z","msg":"168<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c94691b1f31bf8cbb73efebd2ad2abf7643863b","tid":701291,"uid":133529,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:35:22.000Z","msg":"咁似D戒丁POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60019b2357956b386cea4097f5260f21a30b2536","tid":701291,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:36:27.000Z","msg":"撑到頭2個星期就易過"},{"pid":"cb72e431114f64841749a0264db57481e0aabc9a","tid":701291,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T04:45:35.000Z","msg":"唔洗日日跑既 一星期2,3次夠啦<