3332b02b","tid":701291,"uid":21292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:45:41.000Z","msg":"如果男仔減肥，最好加d 阻力運動去維持肌肉，一黎瘦左肌肉細埋都唔好睇，二黎就算以後食物+運動都冇控制好都唔易反彈<br />\n一開始你運動量唔多其實唔洗太在意磅，食野+飲水/屙尿屎/運動出汗可能已經有重量改變，最緊要係build up 健康既生活習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3ec0246606b98ec89d3462126741ec01c54ae3","tid":701291,"uid":53189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T01:27:53.000Z","msg":"巴打幾歲？<br />\n身高體重同你差唔多<br />\n放工返到屋企已經累到唔想落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw聽人講過好似話你運動嘅頭三十分鐘係用緊肝糖<br />\n肝糖用晒先到開始燃燒脂肪<br />\n所以十五分鐘係無用<br />\n不如急步行左半個鐘或依半個鐘做小小肌肉訓練再跑步效果好d"},{"pid":"be351b8352aea0a9770fd9ce1af45478e18c2d19","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:01:22.000Z","msg":"岩岩跑完 26:33秒停左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原本打算跑15分鐘左右完啦<br />\n點知臨完見到有個60-70歲既呀伯 轉左入黎緩跑徑<br />\n<br />\n著住件灰色雞翼袖跑到身水身汗 見到佢咁有魄力就試下跟著佢跑一陣啦 本來諗住跑到對面出口（2-3分鐘就完）<br />\n<br />\n點知跑跑下跑多左10分鐘出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家好撚攰 要快啲沖涼買腿蛋治返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ff3c5a4dd71db0707fffdf87d915b83fab87ad","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f3ec0246606b98ec89d3462126741ec01c54ae3","tid":701291,"uid":53189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T01:27:53.000Z","msg":"巴打幾歲？<br />\n身高體重同你差唔多<br />\n放工返到屋企已經累到唔想落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw聽人講過好似話你運動嘅頭三十分鐘係用緊肝糖<br />\n肝糖用晒先到開始燃燒脂肪<br />\n所以十五分鐘係無用<br />\n不如急步行左半個鐘或依半個鐘做小小肌肉訓練再跑步效果好d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:03:05.000Z","msg":"廿頭啦 岩岩跑左五個字發現原來自己都幾後生下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我諗下星期應該跑到半個鐘掛<br />\n<br />\n陣間google乜係肝糖先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcfd4a6c4f81fea1dc5c48bd6c629519f364baf","tid":701291,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:09:48.000Z","msg":"66kg好肥咩?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:重你6kg"},{"pid":"05229ed07066c8a7cfdacd8e6070b7d7b992a86d","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:34:27.000Z","msg":"再磅： 66kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實希望兩個月到62-63okay架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fec2cd17027320aff9fef5319d7951c9c1df1b","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fcfd4a6c4f81fea1dc5c48bd6c629519f364baf","tid":701291,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:09:48.000Z","msg":"66kg好肥咩?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:重你6kg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"見到自己有雙下巴 食完飯個腩又好突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又鐘意著淨色野 唔減下唔得<br />\n<br />\n同埋有駝背 肩同腰都易酸痛 想改善埋"},{"pid":"db0a0613a06398b08e1526709e43e9ff1eb2200e","tid":701291,"uid":46333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:38:34.000Z","msg":"168 算把啦 操出黎都唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b32cdacba151fed1f86ca0b622516c3c3bfaa50","tid":701291,"uid":53588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db0a0613a06398b08e1526709e43e9ff1eb2200e","tid":701291,"uid":46333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:38:34.000Z","msg":"168 算把啦 操出黎都唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:56:43.000Z","msg":"我都想講 168 操到成身肌肉都無用<br />\n<br />\n諗方法賺多d錢好過"},{"pid":"0fc0252708a267b9e3bfa50490f0bb0a6d42c9f8","tid":701291,"uid":3283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T05:17:31.000Z","msg":"加油 慢慢進步"},{"pid":"d8fcb76bb4179c714b92b94560dbf7db8a5a1dc0","tid"