:"2018-06-16T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"唔夠意志力長做就冇用"},{"pid":"ed5b6b0b018bc25134d9faa55a0b42a66c120909","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T01:41:14.000Z","msg":"Day4: <br />\n磅重： 65.3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n邁向64關口喇！"},{"pid":"e87825e39bcd2704394f9d40bfd0d036b2461474","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:41:43.000Z","msg":"Day:5 64.8<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n琴日咩都冇做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瘋狂訓同飲水 <br />\n但今日跌穿64<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢個重量四年黎冇見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6fbdcbde3bea038e1fec476c945e6c17e10492","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T15:48:29.000Z","msg":"死死氣落去跑<br />\n<br />\n31分鐘 隻腳前所未有咁酸 個人有啲暈<br />\n<br />\n今晚要食m記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw今晚係64.9<br />\n<br />\nDay6黎個階段小結先"},{"pid":"904743a84007697b1586f838750d2461ff5d8832","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T02:43:37.000Z","msg":"今日day6<br />\n<br />\nDay1-day6:<br />\n<br />\n66.5kg -&gt; 65.2 <br />\n最低係64.8<br />\n<br />\n每飲汽水 正常三餐 冇宵夜<br />\n四日運動 由15分 26分 35分 31分<br />\n每次跑完 做左1下引體（正手）3-5set咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下個week開始就想 keep住 隔日跑 即係 跑三次 每次半個鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n每次都盡量試下連續做兩下引體 <br />\n<br />\n飲野方面有得走甜就走 但忍唔住會飲維他奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n目標係落到64kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6081e5557a4065916db23b27724d22224b4f3d37","ti