ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"加油呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跑步你keep住跑就可以越跑越多<br />\n建議你去下gym room，肌肉可以幫你燃燒更多能量，仲有個人有啲線條會更加好睇<br />\n試下一日至多飲一包維他奶，其他飲品就完全唔飲<br />\n記得飲多啲水呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:36:44.000Z","msg":"感謝！<br />\n我打算呢個月都keep住跑先呀<br />\n<br />\n下個月就係公園做多啲fitness啦 因為都唔係太鍾意呢係室內"},{"pid":"d9afe7fc9138432d8a3852ae044b022a2533d2b4","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60960cb2c6bcd4326fc425fd8842d516def67263","tid":701291,"uid":61678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:10:58.000Z","msg":"體重係冇意思"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:39:11.000Z","msg":"冇呀 呢幾日都比較chur 冇乜心機紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6e1106a8c8b53679542503629341978387d7f8","tid":701291,"uid":98099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e439172f00077d9e2e5470cf30eadcd08c79560","tid":701291,"uid":153531,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/16/102535_6d78bc56af4ae4bc012a62fce803fd2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F16%2F102535_6d78bc56af4ae4bc012a62fce803fd2a.png&h=9803de98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n25歲，身高182cm，一星期紀錄一次。因為趕結婚個身形再咁落去影相就柒，決心減肥。小學開始都已經係肥仔，中五有瘦返一段時間大約92kg。<br />\n<br />\n始終都市人生活唔會咁多時間運動，一開始gym room跑步機每日20分鐘都想死。後尾越加越多，再轉成跑街，到依家就先做gym一個鐘，做完出去戶外跑10公里，一星期最少都有6日。養成習慣慢慢加上去。<br />\n<br />\n當然配合埋飲食，早餐茶記叫乜都得野飲少甜/走甜、午餐白魚蛋麵、晚餐食條蒸魚/雞胸。<br />\n<br />\n目標9月前減到80kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:59:42.000Z","msg":"巴打我同你一樣高，90kg <br />\n中學75kg到，中學後冇做運動到呢家幾年肥到依家<br />\n食量明明冇變都keep 住肥...<br />\n都唔知點減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7237df49772b4de111cf8be813fdf4c592dadda4","tid":701291,"uid":43013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/185553_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F185553_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0b09132a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴打我同你一差唔多<br />\n我由中學畢業就冇做運動<br />\n跟住幾年後條脊骨痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(本身我有少少側彎)<br />\n跟住宜家每日都做一次體育堂個種熱身去拉筋 宜家感覺冇咁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過起碼要做一年先有效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873eb647af1762026b0b49430b3ff6aaa044e6b0","tid":701291,"uid":83101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:37:04.000Z","msg":"175cm, 83 kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一拍拖就半年肥左13kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87bbb874a7e86c6bd68913eb34d4c48f4d51ebcf","tid":701291,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T13:21:38.000Z","msg":"兩個月想有變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我踩單車踩左兩個月左右,體重完全冇變過,但運動能力強左好多,未踩之前簡直就係垃圾,雖然而家都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ec54e90b579f9ec30de3262ff8d9bf0f4336cb","tid":701291,"uid":67089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:01:41.000Z","msg":"我就冇你地咁on9,又戒呢樣又戒果樣,反而食多左飯,澱粉唔可以減,跑得越劇烈,越用得多glucose,你如果唔跑得劇烈d練速度,一直慢慢跑,你永遠都咁慢,跑唔快,消秏既能量就越少。以我踩單車為例子,因為新手關係,我係zone 2度踩,輸出大概係100Watt,一小時只消到300幾卡,而pro cyclist zone 2輸出成300 watt,一個鐘就消左成千卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好理自己幾重,有進步就ok,想知點先可以進步得快d,就買d關於長跑訓練既書,唔好亂練。<br />\n我係用zwift來訓練,可以跑步可以踩單車<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wYloq-jS_V4&amp;t=192s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwYloq-jS_V4%26t%3D192s&d=q3Ak43684UhECaN9%2FTJep4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=daec1856\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wYloq-jS_V4&amp;t=192s</a>"},{"pid":"4b706268ff81c0042a9ad3556121f4e3c2a51cc1","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"Day10: 64.9<br />\n<br />\n琴晚當交功課咁跑左半個鐘<br />\n今日起身除左大脾後側有啲酸 其他都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個肥仔波好似瘦左 實小左左 但明明冇做掌上壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e8d8879072c036861c8aefecd7f5bc5471058b","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:32:26.000Z","msg":"Day 11: 食左好多野<br />\n<br />\n65.2<br />\n<br />\n今晚跑跑佢 試下加下量"},{"pid":"2abcfc7d29dbe268201662b71a8c37fde758b58d","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T06:57:52.000Z","msg":"Day:12 64.6<br />\n<br />\n發覺減重果part  離自己目標都幾快 （63，64）<br />\n<br />\n而家跑轉半個鐘完左隻腳都唔會話太酸 黎緊目標係35-40分鐘啦<br />\n<br />\n所以應該改一星期跑兩次 再約下朋友踢下波<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返工方面好似冇以前咁易攰 放工都諗緊今晚有咩節目（但最後都係返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n肩又好似冇咁酸<br />\n<br />\n但寒背唔知有冇改善到<br />\n<br />\n大概係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c15a52ad81a907714327b516d0fe55faf1feea1d","tid":701291,"uid":191539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T07:15:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c132451c3f1e8e802c65f946d67aa57ab96fd6f","tid":701291,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c15a52ad81a907714327b516d0fe55faf1feea1d","tid":701291,"uid":191539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T07:15:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:05:35.000Z","msg":"有用Apple watch <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平均一日消700-800卡路里<br />\n但對食既野未太有概念<br />\n放工list out下平時食咩先"}]}